\begin_layout Section
Designed
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Ian's I
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
This drill was presented by former Michigan State's Spartan Marching Band
 Drum Major Ian McNabb during the 2019 Drum Major Clinic.
\begin_inset Foot
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Ethan will tell you he came up with the name but I'm 100% positive I came
 up with it.
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The drill makes an 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

I
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 shape and should be done while traversing forwards.
 This drill is best taught by teaching the first line, then appending the
 second line, and so forth until the whole drill is marched in one go.
\begin_inset VSpace defskip
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\noindent
\begin_inset Box Frameless
position "t"
hor_pos "c"
has_inner_box 1
inner_pos "t"
use_parbox 0
use_makebox 0
width "100col%"
special "none"
height "1in"
height_special "totalheight"
thickness "0.4pt"
separation "3pt"
